line_1: At market oft for game I search,
line_2: Oft at assemblies, oft at church,

line_1: Though not a grace appears on strictest search,
line_2: But that she fasts, and item, goes to church.

line_1: Straight back you'll turn, vex'd with the fruitless Search;
line_2: Bid ROBERT call a Chair, and go to Church.

line_1: Around the world to find the wretch I'd search,
line_2: Who dares to leave a woman in the lurch. —
